title: The First Ever Radio Hour - 5/2/22
itunes:title: The First Ever Radio Hour - 5/2/22
description:
On this weeks radio hour Jeremy plays new music from Joyce Manor, Truth Cult, Phoebe Bridgers, and Koyo. You’ll also hear tracks from MSPAINT, Gel, Soul Blind, Fleshwater, Webbed Wing, Kevin Devine, Spice, and more!

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early! You'll also see a complete list of songs played on this episode.

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
